{"tid":2364951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【5.27 反國歌法】三青年被指堵路　一人准自簽 2000 元守行為兩年獲撤控","createTime":"2021-01-13T11:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:20:31.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7be95179b8c61c9b0953d467a8fe14d5c095600","tid":2364951,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"為阻止立法會恢復《國歌條例草案》二讀，大批市民去年 5 月下旬在金鐘及中環一帶示威，逾 360 人被捕。其中 3 名男子分別被控非法集結、堵路及襲警等罪，今午（ 13 日）在九龍城法院再訊，其中一名被告獲准以自簽 2000 元、守行為 24 個月方式了事，相關控罪獲撤回。<br />\n<br />\n至於案中其餘兩人，控方指會繼續起訴，但由於辯方仍未收妥涉案警員的書面供詞，故案件押後至下月 10 日再訊。"},{"pid":"89100246caea0d05f1f112a4680d1e6989a34889","tid":2364951,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/5-27-%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF-%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%86%E8%87%AA%E7%B0%BD-2000-%E5%85%83%E5%AE%88%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%A4%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-27-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD-2000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%25A4%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=36d44645\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F5-27-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B0%25BD-2000-%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25AE%2588%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5